Package: brclimate
Type: Package
Title: Scrape Brazilian Historical Climate Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Gustavo", "Carvalho", email = "gustavo.bio@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Get historical climate data from over 1000 climate stations located
    in Brazil. The package include a set of tools for
scraping data from INPE (http: //sinda.crn2.inpe.br/PCD/SITE/novo/site/
    index.php).
License: GPL
LazyData: TRUE
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Imports: rvest,
    httr,
    tidyr,
    dplyr
Depends: R (>= 3.2.4)
